Maryade Prashne" is a slice-of-life, gripping story of strugglers in Bengaluru that explores the power of friendship and the lengths one would go to seek justice for a loved one. Set in the lower middle-class neighborhood of Chamrajpete in Bengaluru, the film follows the journey of three close friends‚ÄîSuri, Manja, and Sathish‚Äîwhose survival is challenged by Rocky, Shetty and his friends.

Maryade Prashne" is a slice-of-life, gripping story of strugglers in Bengaluru that explores the power of friendship and the lengths one would go to seek justice for a loved one. Set in the lower middle-class neighborhood of Chamrajpete in Bengaluru, the film follows the journey of three close friends‚ÄîSuri, Manja, and Sathish‚Äîwhose survival is challenged by Rocky, Shetty and his friends.

snippet.title: Pushpa 2 - The Rule Massive Events Update | Allu Arjun | Sukumar | Rashmika | Devi Sri Prasad
snippet.description:
Pushpa 2 - The Rule Massive Events Update On Mythri Movie Makers.

Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Written and Directed by Sukumar. Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y. Ravi Shankar of Mythri Movie Makers in association with Sukumar Writings. The film stars Allu Arjun, Fahadh Faasil, Rashmika Mandanna, Dhanunjay, Rao Ramesh, Sunil, Anasuya Bharadwaj & Ajay Ghosh. The film's music is composed by Devi Sri Prasad, with cinematography and editing performed by Miroslaw Kuba Brozek and Navin Nooli respectively.

snippet.title: Baaka - The Lake Monster | Take A Break Horror Specials
snippet.description:
Get ready for a spine-chilling and laugh-out-loud adventure with "Baaka - The Lake Monster"! üßü‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏èüíÄüòÇ. In this unique horror-comedy, four friends take a daring trip to the eerie town of Khandoli, home to a sinister legend. The infamous Baaka, a terrifying lake monster, lurks in the dark waters, ready to capture anyone who dares to wander too close to the lake's edge. Once Baaka claims a victim, he doesn‚Äôt stop at drowning them‚Äîhe takes over their body, turning them into his eerie puppet.
In a bold feat, Sharan steps up to prove he‚Äôs not afraid, venturing too close to the haunted lake and ultimately falling under Baaka‚Äôs dark spell. But just when it seems Baaka‚Äôs about to claim another set of victims, the friends have an unexpected trick up their sleeves: they offer the monster some alcohol as part of the dare! What follows is a hilarious twist as Baaka, tipsy and disoriented, dozes off and wakes up miles away from his beloved lake, lost in an unfamiliar town.
Will Baaka wreak havoc in this new town, or will he find his way back to the lake? Join us for a wild ride of suspense, laughs, and unexpected turns as Baaka navigates a world beyond Khandoli. Don‚Äôt miss "Baaka - The Lake Monster" for a dose of horror with a comedic twist! üé¨üëπ

snippet.title: 2nd T20I | Highlights | New Zealand Tour Of Sri Lanka | 10th November 2024
snippet.description:
Sri Lanka and New Zealand went against each other in the 2nd T20I at the Rangiri Dambulla International Stadium. Sri Lanka won the toss and elected to bowl first. New Zealand had a tough time with the bat and kept on losing wickets. In the end, the visitors became all-out for just 108 runs. Sri Lankan batters faced the same issue and ended up with just 103 runs allowing New Zealand to secure a 5-run win in this low-scoring thriller and level the series 1 - 1.
.
.

Credits:-

Song - Kamariya Lollypop
Singer :- Khesari Lal Yadav & Shilpi Raj
Feat :- Namrita Malla
Film Name:- Rajaram
Film Director:- Parag Patil
Song Director :- Sooraj Katoch (Zenith)
Lyrics :- Prakash Barood
Music :- Vinay Vinayak 
Director: - Sooraj Katoch (Zenith)
Choreographer: - Geeta Tamta (Zenith)
DOP- Rahul Yadav 
Editor: - Anand Kumar (Santu)
Associate Dop - Priyanshu Vats 
Focus Puller- Chandan Singh
Dance troupe: - Zenith
Dance Group :- (PK) Kamlesh 
DI :- Rohit Singh 
Production: - Amit Singh
All Costume:- Reema (Zai fashion )
Makeup Hair:- Vikash Kumar and Aryan Rajesh

Film Credits:
Production:- Technician Film Factory 
Producers: - Parag Patil & R.R. Prince

Lyrics:-

Mere figure pe deke dhyan,
Kyon hota hai re munde pareshaan...2
Nasha mein dubal jawani hai,
Khatta angur ka paani hai,
Mera chhikh lage aluchap,
Kamariya..2 Lollypop pop,pop,pop...2

Na na na na na re, Najro se pila dungi,
Ja ja ja ja ja ja re Aaj jila jila dungi,
Tohara se jada Nasha, na baawe daaru mein,
Jawan tu de debu maja u na ba mehraru mein,
Josh mein hosh gawa doge,
Humko note nawa doge,
Jab Dance karungi hip hop,
Kamariya..2 Lollypop pop,pop,pop...2

Laakho diwane yaha aate hain kuch na karke jaate hain,
Pite hain sab kuch khate hain aa bigad ke jaate hain,
Pahile se bigdal baani,
Humke auri bigade da,
Aaj duniya dikha ke babuniya,
Sara garmi jhare da,
Chalo kahi ab chalte hain,
Tere pyar mein dhalte hain,
Karenge khub gup sup,
Kamariya..2 Lollypop pop,pop,pop...2
